short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirects "mo/" links to molinks.me to allow very short links - specific to your organization

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Provides super simple and super easy short links for anything and everything. Keep them private to you or share them with an organization.

Just type mo/whatever-you-want and create the mo link. Or use the extension popup for even faster creation using the current tab URL

Other members of your organization will also need to add the "Mo Links" extension for proper functioning.
